def label2numpy(label):
    fname = f'../{label}_lte_2d_timeseries.npy'
    ngdf_fname = f'../{label}_lte_cell.geojson'

    if os.path.isfile(fname):
        rvals = np.load(fname)

    if os.path.isfile(ngdf_fname):
        new_gdf = gpd.read_file(ngdf_fname)
        new_gdf.crs = original_crs
    
    return new_gdf, rvals

import numpy as np

def cosine_similarity(vector1, vector2):
    dot_product = np.dot(vector1, vector2)
    magnitude1 = np.sqrt(np.sum(np.square(vector1)))
    magnitude2 = np.sqrt(np.sum(np.square(vector2)))
    
    if magnitude1 == 0 or magnitude2 == 0:
        return -1
    
    return dot_product / (magnitude1 * magnitude2)
